00:02:24.180 --> 00:02:25.763
There's a business
value to the things

00:02:25.763 --> 00:02:27.620
that we've done in
the autism community

00:02:27.620 --> 00:02:30.050
really to help those families.

00:02:30.050 --> 00:02:31.490
People will be loyal.

00:02:31.490 --> 00:02:33.590
They will bend over
backwards when you really

00:02:33.590 --> 00:02:38.579
support them and support them in
taking care of their families.

00:02:38.579 --> 00:02:40.370
I'm also proud of the
work we do at Google.

00:02:40.370 --> 00:02:42.036
